726094f-a.title: Queens: Astoria Boulevard - 90th Street
726094f-a.text:
Astoria Boulevard, at the southwest corner of 90th Stre-t,
showing old Public zchool No. 10, also known at one time as
the Bowery Bay District School and the Erogtown chool. It
was erected in 1879.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection  May, 1923

726095f-b.title: Queens: Astoria Boulevard - 90th Street
726095f-b.text:
Astoria Boulevard, at the S. E. corner of 90th Street, showing
the Old Frogtown School which was also known as the Bowery Bay Dis-
trict School. It was erected in 1879 and was still standing in
1927 when it was known as P. S. N0. 10. This is a set of two views.
May 1923
Views 1,2
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
